description: Outline planning application for a mixed use development delivered as a phased masterplan comprising 7 development zones and accommodating up to 178,102 sqm of research & development, offices and other business uses (Use Class B1) in 6 - 13 storey buildings; up to 373 residential units (Use Class C3) in 18 - 32 storey buildings; a hotel up to 8 storeys and associated facilities (Use Class C1); community and/or leisure uses and retail, cafes, restaurants and bars (Use Classes D1 and/or D2, A1-5) together with access, bridge over the railway (Central Line), parking, servicing and landscaping; and the demolition of Stadium House.
